And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row1UIGroup00004Row1Row1Tile1Icon138"

And I close "Assets" window

And I click the button named "FormCreate"

And I close "Fixed assets reconciliations" window

And I click the button named "FormCreate"

And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row1UIGroup00001Row2Row2Tile3Icon207"

** Cataloage
* Gestiune
And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row2UIGroup00002Row1Row1Tile1Icon078"
Then "Locations" window is opened
And I click the button named "FormCreate"
Then "Location (create)" window is opened
And I close "Location (create)" window
Then "Locations" window is opened
And I close "Locations" window
* Clasificstor de active fixe
And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row2UIGroup00002Row2Row2Tile1Icon079"

And I click the button named "FormCreate"
Then "Fixed assets classifier (create)" window is opened
And I close "Fixed assets classifier (create)" window
Then "Fixed assets classifier" window is opened
And I close "Fixed assets classifier" window
** Rapoarte
* Fișa a imobilizării necorporale
And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row2UIGroup00003Row1Row1Tile1Icon112"
Then "Intangible asset card" window is opened
And in "IntangibleAssetCard" spreadsheet document I move to "R1C1" cell
And I close "Intangible asset card" window
* Registru imobilizărilor necorporale
And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row2UIGroup00003Row1Row1Tile2Icon113"
Then "Intangible assets book" window is opened
And in "ReportSpreadsheetDocument" spreadsheet document I move to "R1C1" cell
And I close "Intangible assets book" window
* Graficul de amortizări pentru imobilizările necorporale
And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row2UIGroup00003Row1Row1Tile3Icon114"
Then "Amortization schedule of intangible asset" window is opened
And in "IntangibleAssetSchedule" spreadsheet document I move to "R1C1" cell
And I close "Amortization schedule of intangible asset" window
* Fișa de inventara imobilizărilor corporale/necorporale
And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row2UIGroup00003Row2Row2Tile1Icon109"
Then "Fixed asset card" window is opened
And in "FixedAssetCard" spreadsheet document I move to "R1C1" cell
And I close "Fixed asset card" window
* Registru de inventar a imobilizărilor corporale / necorpora
And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row2UIGroup00003Row2Row2Tile2Icon110"
Then "Fixed assets book" window is opened
And in "ReportSpreadsheetDocument" spreadsheet document I move to "R1C1" cell
And I close "Fixed assets book" window

And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu004Row2UIGroup00003Row2Row2Tile3Icon111"
